name: Members/Military admission to the dance
description: We are having a Mardi Gras Dance at the YMCA Fairgrounds on February 9 2008, 6:00pm to 9:00pm for 5th through 8th grade. Your Ticket includes admittance to the dance, a refreshment and treat, Mardi Gras beads, and Mask. By purchasing your ticket in advance you save a $1.00 off the price. Print out your receipt and bring your Military or YMCA ID with you for admittance to this event.
